      "asbval:drift_notes": [
        "The task card focuses narrowly on the 'impute command' as a discrete implementation task, while the paper describes imputation as one step within a larger quality control workflow. The card's framing as an implementation task ('Implement the imputation filter step') is narrower than the paper's scope, which presents pcpfm as a complete end-to-end pipeline.",
        "The card does not mention other tools used in the pipeline (Asari, Khipu, MatchMS, etc.) that are central to the paper's contribution, suggesting the extractor may have focused on a single component rather than the holistic pipeline design."
