      "asbval:note": "Paper confirms pipeline ingests mzML and raw files, but does not explicitly describe ionization polarity inference as a documented task. The paper does not mention extracting or inferring ionization mode from file headers as a distinct preprocessing step.",
      "asbval:perspicacite_kb": "asb-paper-10-1371-journal-pcbi-1011912",
      "asbval:supported_raw": "partial",
