      "asbval:evidence_quote": null,
      "asbval:note": "Paper does not discuss ionization mode inference as a prerequisite for empirical compound grouping or MS annotation. The paper describes empirical compounds and annotation workflows but does not mention ionization polarity as a required input or decision point.",
