      "asbval:note": "The paper confirms that blank masking, batch correction, and missing value imputation are implemented in pcpfm, but ThermoRawFileParser is a file format converter, not a curation tool. The related_skills list appears to conflate ThermoRawFileParser (a format converter) with the broader curation pipeline. ThermoRawFileParser's actual role is limited to format conversion; the listed skills belong to pcpfm/Asari/metDataModel ecosystem, not to ThermoRawFileParser itself.",
