      "@type": "asbval:ClaimAssessment",
      "asbval:evidence_quote": "Our pipeline, named the Python-centric pipeline for metabolomics (pcpfm), enables start-to-finish metabolomics data processing... The inputs to our pipeline minimally consist of .mzML or .raw files and a metadata CSV file, that minimally maps sample names to acquisition file paths.",
      "asbval:note": "PCPFM is confirmed as the orchestrating pipeline. Batch correction is part of the workflow, though the specific command name 'batch_correct' is not explicitly mentioned in passages.",
